    "description": "In Wired Gambit, you and Smuggy take turns cutting wires on a bomb. Only one wire triggers the explosion, and your goal is to avoid it. Use your items to gain shields, test wires, double the bomb's damage, skip turns, or even cut a wire let Smuggy face the consequences! <br><br>Outsmart Smuggy with cunning tactics and manage your resources to survive this high-stakes challenge!<br><br>The game features a basic Standard Mode, which unlocks 8 Challenge Modes and an Endless Mode upon first completion. <br><br>In Endless Mode, complete as many rounds as possible, but beware—if you don't claim your score and end up perishing, it will be lost!<br>Every new round is a chance to either increase your score, or lose it all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009080/extras/c3ebe079293422c31a439903f2163084.poster.avif?t=1721616401\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009080/extras/c3ebe079293422c31a439903f2163084.webm?t=1721616401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009080/extras/c3ebe079293422c31a439903f2163084.mp4?t=1721616401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
